--- Third-Party Dependencies ---

This project depends on third-party open source packages.
Each package retains its own license terms. Key runtime dependencies include:

  - ink (MIT) — React for terminals
  - react (MIT) — UI library
  - openai (Apache-2.0) — OpenAI API client
  - undici (MIT) — HTTP client
  - zod (MIT) — Schema validation
  - ejs (Apache-2.0) — Template engine
  - chalk (MIT) — Terminal string styling
  - gradient-string (MIT) — Gradient text
  - gray-matter (MIT) — YAML frontmatter parser
  - ignore (MIT) — .gitignore parser

A complete and up-to-date list is available in package.json.
Run `npm ls --all --production` for the full dependency tree with license metadata.

